{Black prepares to develop his dark-squared bishop.} 12. Bd3 Nd4 13. Kb1 Ne2 14. 
Qf3 Ba3 {A nice tactical trick.} 15. bxa3 Nc3+ 16. Kc1 Nxa2+ {Black is winning.} 
*

