is known Scotch Gambit. White sacrifices a pawn in order to achieve fast 
development.} Bc5 {Black develops and protects his pawn on d4.} 5. c3 {c3 
transposes to the Italian Game after...} Nf6 {We have transposed to the Italian 
Game.} *

